{
  "name": "Superior Cooking Tool",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/symbols/cross-circle-blue.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Category: Class</p><p>Prerequisite: At least 4+ levels in Cooking Nin. </p><p><br />Your time working with your cooking tool allows you to enhance its potential. <br />you gain the following benefits:</p><p> </p><p>• Either of your Cooking Tools from either Cooking Tool Infusion or Bonus Tool Infusion gains an extra property from its first set of properties. </p><p>• at 8th level, the Cooking Tool you chose for the first extra property gains a second property from its second set of properties. </p><p>• at 12th level the Cooking Tool you chose for the first and second extra property gains a second property from its third set of properties. </p><p>• this feat can be taken a second time giving both your your Cooking Tools the extra properties.</p>",
